entry.tran: （在学业或工作上）过于强求成功，过于争强好胜
entry.def: If someone overachieves in something such as school work or a job, they work very hard, especially in a way that makes them tired or unhappy. They want to be successful because it is very important to them to do well and not because they enjoy what they are doing.
